"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-pressbox-press-releases-tickets-for-nbc-television-networks-live-coverage-of-the-2024-paris-olympics-opening-ceremony-in-imax-locations-nationwide-now-on-sale-at-fandango\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Los Angeles, CA - June 26, 2024- Starting today, tickets are now available on Fandango for the NBC television network's live coverage of the 2024 Paris Olympics Opening Ceremony in IMAX locations nationwide - the first time ever the global event will be presented live in IMAX.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 78, \"end\": 86, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fandango_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.547958918732188e-29, \"text\": \"Fandango\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fandango_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fandango_Media\"}, {\"begin\": 95, \"end\": 98, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9983236730818235, \"rank\": 0.0016771628360105412, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Friends and families can gather together for a unique and immersive theatre experience and enjoy what promises to be one of the most spectacular Opening Ceremonies in Olympic history.\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 461, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2024 Paris Olympics Opening Ceremony will be presented live in more than 150 IMAX locations throughout the United States on Friday, July 26th.\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 573, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999987948128229, \"rank\": 1.2052016824667077e-05, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year, the Paris Olympics Opening Ceremony is making history by taking place on one of the world's most famous waterways, the River Seine.\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 625, \"end\": 639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 640, \"end\": 656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.8452978829947074, \"rank\": 0.18224917330131013, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games_ceremony\"}, {\"begin\": 740, \"end\": 751, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organizers plan to transform this iconic River into the world's largest theatrical stage for what promises to be one of the most spectacular Opening Ceremonies in Olympic history.\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 932, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of walking into a stadium, a four-mile-long flotilla of nearly 100 boats will carry athletes from more than 200 countries past hundreds of thousands of spectators seated on the banks of the Seine.\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1131, \"end\": 1136, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999998919443046, \"rank\": 1.0778078208911772e-07, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to the recentFandango 2024 Moviegoing Trends and Insights Studyof more than 6,000 moviegoers, premium formats, such as IMAX, continue to be big motivators for experiencing entertainment on the big screen.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was also uncovered that in addition to theatrical movies, alternative content is also appealing to moviegoers, with 70% of parents surveyed stating they would be interested in experiencing sporting events, such as the Olympics, on the big screen.\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1603, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tickets for NBC television network's coverage of the 2024 Paris Olympics Opening Ceremony in IMAX can be found here onFandango.\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1617, \"end\": 1620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9983236730818235, \"rank\": 0.0016771628360105412, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Link to the trailer ishere.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 1760, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickherefor more programming information about NBCU's coverage of the Olympic Games Paris 2024, scheduled for July 26-Aug. 11.\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1810, \"end\": 1814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ABOUT NBCUNIVERSAL  NBCUniversal is one of the world's leading media and entertainment companies in the development, production, and marketing of entertainment, news, sports and information to a global audience.\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 2102, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1897, \"end\": 1909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.999972614324234, \"rank\": 2.7386425781691607e-05, \"text\": \"NBCUNIVERSAL\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 1911, \"end\": 1923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.999972614324234, \"rank\": 2.7386425781691607e-05, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCUniversal owns and operates a valuable portfolio of news and entertainment television networks, a premier motion picture company, significant television production operations, a leading television stations group, world-renowned theme parks, and a premium ad-supported streaming service.\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2392, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2103, \"end\": 2115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.999972614324234, \"rank\": 2.7386425781691607e-05, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"NBCUniversal is a subsidiary of Comcast Corporation.\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2393, \"end\": 2405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.999972614324234, \"rank\": 2.7386425781691607e-05, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 2425, \"end\": 2444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Comcast Corporation\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Comcast\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"About Fandango  Fandango digital network provides unrivaled, instant access to all things movies and TV, enhancing fan enjoyment across the entire entertainment journey.\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2616, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2453, \"end\": 2461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fandango_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.547958918732188e-29, \"text\": \"Fandango\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fandango_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fandango_Media\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The portfolio serves more than 50 million unique visitors per month and includes leading online movie ticketer, Fandango, which tickets for 31,000 U.S. movie screens; world-renowned entertainment review site, Rotten Tomatoes; and Fandango at Home, the on-demand streaming service offering the industry's best selection of 4K UHD titles and more than 250,000 new release and catalogue movies and next day TV shows.\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 3030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2729, \"end\": 2737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fandango_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.547958918732188e-29, \"text\": \"Fandango\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fandango_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fandango_Media\"}, {\"begin\": 2826, \"end\": 2841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rotten_Tomatoes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rotten Tomatoes\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rotten_Tomatoes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rotten_Tomatoes\"}, {\"begin\": 2847, \"end\": 2855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fandango_Media\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.547958918732188e-29, \"text\": \"Fandango\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fandango_Media\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fandango_Media\"}, {\"begin\": 2939, \"end\": 2945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/4K_resolution\", \"score\": 0.8311706155437484, \"rank\": 0.2031224171050964, \"text\": \"4K UHD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/4K_resolution\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/4K_resolution\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ABOUT IMAX CORPORATION  IMAX, an innovator in entertainment technology, combines proprietary software, architecture, and equipment to create experiences that take you beyond the edge of your seat to a world you have never imagined.\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Top filmmakers and studios are utilizing IMAX systems to connect with audiences in extraordinary ways, making IMAX's network among the most important and successful theatrical distribution platforms for major event films around the globe.\", \"from\": 3264, \"to\": 3502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3374, \"end\": 3378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IMAX\", \"score\": 0.9999999943102011, \"rank\": 5.6898345536467616e-09, \"text\": \"IMAX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IMAX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/IMAX\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Division ofNBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3506, \"end\": 3516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.999999996740371, \"rank\": 3.259519694365731e-09, \"text\": \"A Division\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DISCLAIMER: This site and the products offered are for entertainment purposes only, and there is no gambling offered on this site.\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This service is intended for adult audiences.\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3710, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No guarantees are made for any specific outcome.\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3759, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, please call 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 3760, \"to\": 3837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u24b8 2024 NBC Universal\", \"from\": 3839, \"to\": 3859, \"entities\": []}]}"